metaContent.title: Luxury Cinema Broadgate | Cinema Listings & Tickets
metaContent.description: Everyman Broadgate is redefining cinema - experience the latest movies with luxury sofa seating, amazing food, cocktails & more - book online today!

freeTextShape.html: Located in the heart of London Liverpool Street, Everyman Broadgate features three homely cinema screens, a Spielburger kitchen, and a large bar with a 70s feel.

rows.content:
Tucked beneath Finsbury Avenue Square in the heart of Broadgate Circle, just moments from Liverpool Street Station, Shoreditch, and Spitalfields - our Broadgate cinema blends retro design with modern luxury, for the ultimate cinema experience.

Inside, discover three unique cinema screens featuring our signature sofa and armchair seating, a statement bar, and a relaxed lounge inspired by the 1970s. Take your visit to the next level and enjoy hand-stretched pizzas, premium burgers, sharing plates, indulgent desserts from our famous Spielburger Kitchen, or try something from our drinks menu including wines, cocktails, craft beers, and hot drinks. So whether you enjoy your food & drinks at the bar, or have our waiter service from your seat, every visit is designed to feel special.

Private Events & Cinema hire is also available at Everyman Broadgate, giving you the chance to host an extraordinary event. From corporate presentations, birthday parties, and celebrations our cinema offers a stylish and versatile setting for every occasion. Explore our private hire brochure for Everyman Broadgate today.

Browse our current film listings and book online in advance for the best seats. We are open daily from 10am (or half an hour before the first film of the day, if earlier). For details on accessibility, travel, parking, and screen information, please see the dropdown sections below.

Liverpool Street Station (Central, Circle, Metropolitan and Hammersmith & City Lines)

Moorgate Station (Northern, Circle, Metropolitan and Hammersmith & City Lines)
rows.title: Public transport

rows.content: Broadgate Car Park, underneath Broadwalk House (EC2A 2EW), is open 24/7 with 85 spaces.
rows.title: Parking

rows.content:
Everyman Broadgate has full step-free access for our customers with a lift down from street level. 

There are three removable seats and two wheelchair spaces in Screen 1.

There are two removable seats and a wheelchair space in Screen 2.

There is a wheelchair space in Screen 3, but no removable seats.
rows.title: Disabled access

rows.content: 8am daily (or half an hour before the first film of the day, if earlier).
